[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1463333","time":"2019-7-12 16:40","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"(-Wish upon a Shooting Star-)","message":"占楼做统计用","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1463334","time":"2019-7-12 16:41","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"(-Wish upon a Shooting Star-)","message":"2019/07/12<br>已经确定会做的功能<br>* 支持系统级的黑暗模式，等Android Q和iOS13正式版发布了支持。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1463335","time":"2019-7-12 16:47","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"(-Wish upon a Shooting Star-)","message":"改进的时间线（没有重复内容）<br><br>也许你已经注意到，BangumiN实现了一个可以无限滚动的时间线，而Bangumi只提供了翻页形式的时间线，这其实并不如想象中的那么简单，因为有许多需要考虑的边缘情况<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">（用户很久没有刷新的时候刷新一次，应该清空当前内容并载入最新内容/如果有人删掉了某条时间线，翻页时可能会漏刷/如果时间线前方有没有刷新的内容，用户想刷新旧的时间线，翻页数目此时不可知，需要先获取新的再获取旧的）..等等</span><br><br>目前的逻辑里还有些bug，其中一个表现就是时间线里会出现重复的。<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">其实网页版也是同样的效果，只不过翻到第二页有重复没有无限滚动的下一条有重复那么明显。</span><br><br>修复：一个改进的时间线，不会刷出重复内容","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1463336","time":"2019-7-12 16:47","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"(-Wish upon a Shooting Star-)","message":"原生支持查看人物/角色并回复讨论<br><br>目前会转到网页","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1463337","time":"2019-7-12 16:47","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"(-Wish upon a Shooting Star-)","message":"改进用户主页的设计<br><br>超级丑，暂时没想到好的设计","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/45/18/451869.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1463861","time":"2019-7-13 23:15","userId":"ttsuxx","userName":"颓痴先生。","userSign":"","message":"+1"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1463338","time":"2019-7-12 16:48","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"(-Wish upon a Shooting Star-)","message":"根据网络状况加载图片（wifi优先大图，数据优先小图，或永远优先大图/小图）","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1463339","time":"2019-7-12 16:48","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"(-Wish upon a Shooting Star-)","message":"自定义头像是方还是圆<br><br>现在头像全部为圆，可以做一个选项选是方是圆","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1463341","time":"2019-7-12 16:50","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"(-Wish upon a Shooting Star-)","message":"查看通知<br><br>实现一个完整版（查看数目，通知标为已读）并不是很容易，但实现一个简单版（可查看有没有通知，然后转到网页操作）应该并不难，但是需要思考通知图标放在哪里","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/26/342667.jpg","floor":"#9-1","id":"1463375","time":"2019-7-12 18:36","userId":"342667","userName":"鋭ちゃん","userSign":"","message":"+1,这个对我超级重要"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/45/18/451869.jpg","floor":"#9-2","id":"1463853","time":"2019-7-13 23:13","userId":"ttsuxx","userName":"颓痴先生。","userSign":"","message":"+1"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/37/04/370405.jpg","floor":"#9-3","id":"1463856","time":"2019-7-13 23:13","userId":"inchei","userName":"茵陳","userSign":"","message":"+1"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/02/250298.jpg","floor":"#9-4","id":"1463900","time":"2019-7-14 02:11","userId":"hupanxx","userName":"Panzerance🀃","userSign":"","message":"有提醒的话右上角头像右上方加个小红点不就好了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#9-5","id":"1463901","time":"2019-7-14 02:15","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Panzerance&#x1F003;</span> 说: 有提醒的话右上角头像右上方加个小红点不就好了</q></div>头像已经有自己的作用了（点击进入设置界面），觉得加一个小红点的话，点一下结果进了设置会让人困惑，设置界面也不适合放通知内容<br>目前看来最有可能放在左上角，或者在最右边的主页tab上显示一个小红点，然后切到主页tab可以看到通知"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#9-6","id":"1472747","time":"2019-8-2 12:33","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"","message":"可以看通知了"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1463342","time":"2019-7-12 16:50","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"(-Wish upon a Shooting Star-)","message":"查看作品与用户统计<br><br>BangumiN的网页版的核心功能之一，目前可以在app里转到网页版，但是也许可以在app里实现一个简略版","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/26/342667.jpg","floor":"#10-1","id":"1463376","time":"2019-7-12 18:36","userId":"342667","userName":"鋭ちゃん","userSign":"","message":"+1"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1463343","time":"2019-7-12 16:52","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"(-Wish upon a Shooting Star-)","message":"可以在发帖前预览发帖渲染效果（可能与实际有差距）<br>目前是纯文本的bbcode <span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">和网页一样也不是不能用</span><br><br>最终目标是做成富文本编辑式的编辑器，完全不用写bbcode，目前使用的框架（flutter）没有提供很好的支持所以暂不考虑。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1463344","time":"2019-7-12 16:53","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"(-Wish upon a Shooting Star-)","message":"作品评论/用户收藏支持倒序查看（如，从评分低到评分高）<br><br>目前只支持正序","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408230.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1463345","time":"2019-7-12 16:54","userId":"408230","userName":"astrea","userSign":"(-Wish upon a Shooting Star-)","message":"可以编辑已经发表的回复","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/26/342667.jpg","floor":"#13-1","id":"1463377","time":"2019-7-12 18:36","userId":"342667","userName":"鋭ちゃん","userSign":"","message":"+1"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/39/09/390977.jpg","floor":"#13-2","id":"1463410","time":"2019-7-12 20:29","userId":"glazygalaxy","userName":"琉宇GlazyGalaxy","userSign":"","message":"+1"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/37/04/370405.jpg","floor":"#13-3","id":"1463852","time":"2019-7-13 23:12","userId":"inchei","userName":"茵陳","userSign":"","message":"+1"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/45/18/451869.jpg","floor":"#13-4","id":"1463859","time":"2019-7-13 23:14","userId":"ttsuxx",